        "<a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Cameron_Disney'>Wikipedia</a>, katsottu 10.9.2025 (Dorothy Cameron Disney: Dorothy Cameron Disney MacKaye (November 13, 1903 – September 5, 1992) was an American mystery writer and journalist who was born in pre-statehood Oklahoma and died in Guilford, Connecticut. Under the Dorothy Cameron Disney byline (the name she also used in fiction writing) she was the creator of the modern marriage advice column.)"@fi ;
